This map is a remix of the orginal map "Surf_Japan" - v10

I did NOT make this map from scratch, i edited the version, changeed textures and rebuilded houses, surfs and things like that, i also added new things, like houses, new jail and a new spawn.

The map is still beta, so please report bugs and things like that, me and my friends have tested the map alot of times and couldt find any bugs.
